          image of the unit square under a matrix transformation.
          Match each matrix in the left column with the corresponding
          image of the unit square.
        </p>

        <figure xml:id="diagram-unit-square">
          <caption>The unit square</caption>
          <image width="40%">
            <prefigure xmlns="https://prefigure.org"
